trailingComments.value:
*
 * 主题详情加载完，会调用此方法告诉客户端该主题信息。android：show-skin-download-btn
 *
 * 支持平台：书旗iOS
 *
 * @param {string} params.themeId - 皮肤id
 * @param {string} params.imgUrl - 皮肤封面图片地址
 * @param {string} params.name - 皮肤名称
 * @param {string} params.size - 皮肤包大小
 * @param {string} params.downloadUrl - 下载地址
 * @param {string} params.desc - 皮肤描述 非必须
 * @param {number} params.type - 皮肤类型
 * @param {string} params.version - 皮肤包版本
 * @param {string} params.shareUrl - 分享地址
 * @param {string} params.shareTitle - 分享标题
 * @param {string} params.shareContent - 分享内容
 *
 * @returns {Promise<*>}
 *
 * @example
 * libSQ.exec('notify-skin-detail-finish', {
 *  params: {
 *     beginTime: "0",
 *     color: "#f0c9ce",
 *     cornerName: "test",
 *     cornerStyle: "0",
 *     coverUrl: "http://img-tailor.11222.cn/pm/app/2017JulThu4ad2fa4e2a66e0ed3959c3933c74fdff.png",
 *     createTime: "1500345061",
 *     downloadCount: 10000,
 *     endTime: "0",
 *     id: "999",
 *     info: '',
 *     name: "默认",
 *     package: {
 *       createTime: "1500544140",
 *       downloadUrl: "222",
 *       id: "62",
 *       infoId: "20",
 *       packageHash: "11",
 *       packageSize: "11",
 *        platform: "1",
 *       skinId: "999",
 *       skinVersion: "11",
 *       status: "1",
 *       updateTime: "1517987725"
 *     },
 *     remark: "自动化专用,请勿修改",
 *     shareUrl: "http://booktouch.demowx.uae.uc.cn#!/ct/skinDetail/sid/999",
 *     skinType: "1",
 *     status: "1",
 *     target: "0",
 *     updateTime: "1517987725"
 *   }
 * }).then((info) => {
 *   alert(`[refresh][notify-skin-detail-finish][then] ${JSON.stringify(info, null, 2)}`);
 * }).catch((err) => {
 *   alert(`[refresh][notify-skin-detail-finish][error] ${JSON.stringify(err, null, 2)}`);
 * });
